Titolo: The Legend of Korra (video game)

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: The Legend of Korra is a 2014 third-person action beat 'em up video game developed by PlatinumGames and published by Activision, based on the animated television series of the same name which aired on Nickelodeon from 2012 to 2014. It was released in October 2014 for PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4, Windows, Xbox 360 and Xbox One, and received mixed reviews.
The game is one of two video games based on the same plot from the series. The other, The Legend of Korra: A New Era Begins, is a turn-based strategy game for the Nintendo 3DS.
Only three years after its release, the game was removed from sale on all digital storefronts on December 21, 2017.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
